query:
INSERT INTO market_order_info AS mol
            (
                structure_id,
                region_id,
                order_id,

                type_id,
                price,
                expires,
                is_buy
            )
            SELECT $1, $2, * FROM UNNEST(
                $3::BIGINT[],
                $4::INTEGER[],
                $5::FLOAT[],
                $6::TIMESTAMP[],
                $7::BOOLEAN[]
            )
            ON CONFLICT (order_id)
            DO UPDATE SET
                expires = EXCLUDED.expires,
                price = EXCLUDED.price
            WHERE mol.expires != EXCLUDED.expires
            OR mol.price != EXCLUDED.price
